        <h3><a href="../comment/19189#comment-19189" class="permalink" rel="bookmark">Gimp Book updated to 1.1.0</a></h3>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>Main changes is support for right-to-left reading, which should be great for manga artists.<br />
Plus, I added .bmp export support, and fixed a number of bugs.</p>
<p>I'm having some trouble uploading the latest version here, so for now you can get it from my site at <a href="http://ragnarb.com/toolbox/gimp-book/">http://ragnarb.com/toolbox/gimp-book/</a></p>
</div></div></div>          </div>
