        <h3><a href="../comment/18201#comment-18201" class="permalink" rel="bookmark">Updated GIMP Book with zoom, margin and bleed guides and more</a></h3>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>Here is the complete list of changes for version 1.0.0.</p>
<p>- Changed versioning to use the more standard, major.minor.patch.<br />
- Added zoom to the page preview, so you can display the pages at different sizes.<br />
- Rewrote the thumbnail generation, and moved thumbs into the book folder.<br />
- Storyboard mode and zoom level are now saved with the book.<br />
- Fixed a bug where exporting non-flattend xcf files, would still flatten them.<br />
- Fixed the layout of the New Book window.<br />
- Added support for defining print resolution when creating new books.<br />
- Added option to create margin and bleed guides on book creation.</p>
</div></div></div>          </div>
  </div>

