        <h3><a href="../comment/18177#comment-18177" class="permalink" rel="bookmark">Gimp Book added OpenRaster support and fixed Windows bug</a></h3>
    
    <div class="content">
      <div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>The latest version fixes the annoying Windows bug introduced after Gimp 2.8.4, that would crash Gimp Book, when you tried to choose a destination folder, either for creating a new book, or for exporting one.</p>
<p>In addition I've added OpenRaster .ora support, both for export and import, to make it easier to jump between Gimp, Krita and MyPaint.</p>
</div></div></div>          </div>
  </div>

