    <div class="content">
      <div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even"><p>I've updated the GIMP Book plug-in to run under Windows. It requires that you have a working version of Python 2.6 along with Gimp 2.6. In addition I fixed a minor bug that would fail if no ~/.thumbnail/large or normal folder existed.</p>
<p>GIMP Book should still be considered beta. I guess I'll move it out of beta when I've used it to create a short comic book. :)</p>
